  "texts": [
    "We generated two distinct visualizations to analyze different relational aspects.",
    "For the first plot, which focuses on geographic proximity, we created a sample of 500 merchants by randomly selecting 50 from each of 10 popular countries/regions.",
    "For the second plot, focusing on business similarity, we created a sample of 500 merchants by selecting 50 from each of 10 popular merchant categories.",
    "The resulting scatter plots are presented in Fig. 8; the top plot visualizes the location-based sample, while the bottom visualizes the category-based sample.Observing the plot for the location-based sample (Fig.",
    "8.top), we see that merchants from the same countries or regions cluster together."
  ],
